### Create a contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Chase",
  "lastName": "Pope",
  "email": "chase@example.com",
  "phone": "208-555-1234"
}

### Update a contact (paste a real id from MongoDB after creating one)
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/6a03cf7de062f88849a1d722
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Chase",
  "lastName": "Pope",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "phone": "208-555-9999"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/6a03cf7de062f88849a1d722